      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NO STOP SIGNS (2) was out of the placings last time when sixth at Horsham (28.51) but scored three back at this track (30.28). Has a solid record over this journey. Won at his only start from this box. Tough to beat if on-song. SOCIALISM (3) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Grade 5 NP winner three back (35.11) at this track over 600m. Can turn it around this time. MAGIC BULLSEYE (1) filled a minor placing last start at Bendigo behind Alligator Rock (28.43) in a Grade 5. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Bold showing expected. PAW JULIA (7) cannot be left out after placing last start.",
